        {"@type": "Question", "name": "Does rose gold require replating like white gold?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "No. Rose gold gets its colour from the copper alloy content, not a surface coating. It maintains its colour without replating. White gold is rhodium-plated and needs replating every 1-5 years; rose gold doesn't."}},
