  },
  {
    q: "What stone shapes work best with rose gold?",
    a: "Oval is the most popular pairing - the warm metal and soft silhouette complement each other naturally. Pear, round, and cushion also pair well. Rose gold is especially suited to vintage-inspired designs where the warm tone reinforces the period aesthetic."
